description: Arnott’s Tim Tam White is a mouth-watering combination of crunchy biscuit, luscious cream centre, wrapped in a creamy chocolate coating. It’s easy to see why Tim Tam is Australia’s most-loved chocolate biscuit.Indulge in true decadence with Arnott’s Tim Tam White chocolate biscuits. Wrapped in a creamy chocolate coating, these biscuits are irresistibly good and the perfect way to indulge in the afternoon or unwind at the end of a long day. What more could you wish for?  • Australia’s most-loved chocolate biscuits. • Wrapped in a creamy chocolate coating. • For your moment of afternoon indulgence. • There is no substitute. • Made in Australia.Australia's most-loved chocolate biscuitsMade in AustraliaThere is no substituteMade with irresistable real chocolate
